{"tid":2008555,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：不能隨意撤銷年輕犯人控罪　請年輕人「潔身自愛」","createTime":"2020-05-09T06:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T11:38:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ddec40c0724fc87ea7378a9e86450c296bd3c627","tid":2008555,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司司長鄭若驊在網誌指，不能隨意以公眾利益為由撤銷年輕犯人的控罪，呼籲年輕人潔身自愛，遠離暴力。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊指過去大半年社會動盪，不少未成年青少年和學生參與違法或暴力活動，有人誤以為年輕人犯罪只會被警司警誡，不留案底，又或可以簽保守行為，但並非所有人均符合條件，需考慮罪行嚴重性或悔意等。<br />\n<br />\n她指檢控人員亦不能隨意以公眾利益為由，撤銷年輕犯人控罪，強調犯案者的年齡並非檢控決定唯一因素，任何人用違法行為達成目的，亦要預備承受法律責任，希望年輕一輩凡事三思而行，不應以身試法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390424&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7dz%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=5b008edd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390424&h=8afdcb41\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390424</a>"},{"pid":"18cdd4cadf052f14133538b1beca4cb36914c742","tid":2008555,"uid":342854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbb0c5a38872c06a4d971116d51c2a4eca0654a","tid":2008555,"uid":194588,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"ddec40c0724fc87ea7378a9e86450c296bd3c627","tid":2008555,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司司長鄭若驊在網誌指，不能隨意以公眾利益為由撤銷年輕犯人的控罪，呼籲年輕人潔身自愛，遠離暴力。<br />\n<br />\